gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 133, Rockets 110
gameRecap.excerpt: Golden State defeats Houston, 133-110. For Golden State, Stephen Curry led the way with 29 points, six rebounds, and six assists with Klay Thompson adding 29 points (seven 3PM) and four assists in the victory. Jabari Smith Jr. finished with 24 points (four 3PM) and three rebounds for Houston in the losing effort. Golden State improves to 42-34, while Houston moves to 38-38 with the loss.
